Class PortalPrepared

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Future<PortalReady>, Associator, Eligible

    public class PortalPrepared
extends CompletionEvent<PortalReady>

    This event is the completion event for the PortalReady event. A portal policy component should handle this event by sending the last known layout to the portal and triggering the rendering of the portlets that are to be displayed in that layout.
